  3
x;\L\C3;MISCELLANEOUS\H0.83333x;\l\C6;\P\pa0.66667,sm1.07917;REFER TO ARCHITECTURAL DRAWINGS FOR WALL OPENINGS, ARCHITECTURAL FEATURES AND DIMENSIONS NOT\P SHOWN.REFER TO MEP DRWINGS FOR SIZE AND LOCATION OF DUCT OPENINGS, PIPING, CONDUITS, ETC. \PNO
