  3
HICK SOLING WITH SAND CUSHION SHALL BE  PROVIDED UNDER RAFT,INDEPENDENT AND COMBINED FOOTINGS IF REQUIRED DEWATERING SHALL BE DONE BY PROVIDING  SUMPS DEEPER THAN THE GENERAL EXCAVATION FOR RAFT BUT BEYOND THE BUILDING LINES.  \P\P\pqd;4.07 REFER SEP
  3
ARATE GENERAL EXCAVATION DRAWING AND SOIL CONSULTANT INPUTS FOR EARTH WORK.\P\pi0,l0,q*;4.08  ALL ABOVE MEASURES TO BE BROUGHT TO THE NOTICE OF SOIL \P           CONSULTANTS  FOR APPROVAL BEFORE EXECUTION.\P4.09   REFER SOIL REPORT BY “BORE TECH SERV
  3
ICES” {\A1;AND          ^J          FOR OTHER  RELEVANT INFORMATION ON EXCAVATION / SHORING, }REFER  \P          SHORING DRAWINGS BY EXTERNAL CONSULTANT.\P         {\A1;\P}4.10   UNLESS OTHERWISE NOTED, 100 THK. PCC WITH CUBE STRENGTH OF \P          M
  3
10 N/MM{\A1;2 SHALL BE PROVIDED ON ALL SOIL SURFACES FORMING THE  \P          BASE FOR STRUCTURAL CONCRETE MEMBERS.\P4.11   FOR EXCAVATION BELOW GROUND WITH WATER SEEPAGES, DEWATERING   \P          SHALL BE DONE TO KEEP THE EXCAVATION PIT ADEQUATELY 
  1
 DRY\P          DURING FORMING AND CASTING THE FOUNDATION.}
